{"name": "yapcache", "metadata": {"name": "yapcache", "version": "0.1.7", "classifiers": ["Framework :: AsyncIO", "Programming Language :: Python", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.12", "Programming Language :: Python :: Implementation :: CPython", "Programming Language :: Python :: Implementation :: PyPy"], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": "https://github.com/ecarrara/yapcache#readme", "dependencies": ["cachebox", "redis", "typing-extensions"], "summary": null, "upload_time": 1735179145}, "documentation": ["# yapcache\n\n[![PyPI - Version](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/yapcache.svg)](https://pypi.org/project/yapcache)\n[![PyPI - Python Version](https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/yapcache.svg)](https://pypi.org/project/yapcache)\n\nYet another Python cache library.\n\n**Table of Contents**\n\n- [Installation](#installation)\n- [Usage](#usage)\n- [License](#license)\n\n## Installation\n\n```console\npip install yapcache\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nIn memory cache:\n\n```python\nimport asyncio\nfrom yapcache import memoize\nfrom yapcache.caches.memory import InMemoryCache\n\ncache = InMemoryCache(maxsize=1_000, key_prefix=f\"example:\")\n\n\n@memoize(cache, ttl=60, cache_key=lambda n: f\"slow-{n}\")\nasync def slow_fn(n: int):\n    await asyncio.sleep(n)\n\n\nasync def example():\n    await slow_fn(3)\n    await slow_fn(3)  # cached!\n\n\nasyncio.run(example())\n```\n\nRedis cache:\n\n```python\n# ...\nfrom redis.asyncio.client import Redis\nfrom yapcache.caches.redis import RedisCache\n\n\nredis_client = Redis()\ncache = RedisCache(redis_client, key_prefix=f\"example:\")\n```\n\nMulti-layer cache:\n\n```python\n# ...\nfrom yapcache.caches import MultiLayerCache\n\nredis_client = Redis()\n\ncache = MultiLayerCache(\n    [InMemoryCache(maxsize=2_000), RedisCache(redis_client)],\n    key_prefix=f\"example:\",\n)\n```\n\nUse `lock` parameter to protect against thundering herd (only one coroutine/thread\nwill do the work and update the cache):\n\n```python\n# ...\nfrom yapcache.distlock import RedisDistLock\n\n@memoize(\n    cache,\n    ttl=60,\n    cache_key=lambda n: f\"slow-{n}\",\n    lock=lambda key: RedisDistLock(redis_client, key),\n)\nasync def slow_fn(n: int):\n    # ...\n```\n\nUse `best_before` to serve stale data (update the cache in background):\n\n```python\n@memoize(\n    cache,\n    ttl=60,\n    cache_key=lambda n: f\"slow-{n}\",\n    best_before=lambda n: time.time() + 30\n)\nasync def slow_fn(n: int):\n    # ...\n```\n\n## License\n\n`yapcache` is distributed under the terms of the [MIT](https://spdx.org/licenses/MIT.html) license.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "yapcache.caches.memory", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "yapcache.caches.memory.InMemoryCache", "bases": ["Cache"], "methods": [{"name": "yapcache.caches.memory.InMemoryCache.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "maxsize", "type": {"name": "int", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.int", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "capacity", "type": {"name": "int", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.int", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "**kwargs", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "yapcache.caches.memory.InMemoryCache.get", "asynchronous": true, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "key", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "CacheItem | NotFound", "xref": null, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "yapcache.caches.memory.InMemoryCache.set", "asynchronous": true, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "key", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "